            <p class="card-text">No idea how to play hangman? Click <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=18&v=cGOeiQfjYPk&feature=emb_logo" target="_blank">this link</a> for a video explaining the basic concepts of the game!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
